sequenceDiagram
  participant AUI as Admin Panel
  participant GW as Gateway
  participant AS as admin-service
  participant US as user-service
  participant ADB as admin postgres
  participant AN as analytics

  AUI->>GW: PUT /api/admin/users/:userId/status
  GW->>AS: status update
  AS->>US: verify admin token
  US-->>AS: admin ok
  AS->>US: PUT /api/users/:userId/status
  US-->>AS: status updated
  AS->>ADB: create ModerationLog
  AS->>AN: emit ADMIN_USER_STATUS_UPDATED
  AS-->>AUI: operation result

  AUI->>GW: PUT /api/admin/users/:userId/preferences/reset
  GW->>AS: reset preferences
  AS->>US: PUT /api/users/:userId/preferences/reset
  US-->>AS: preferences reset
  AS->>ADB: create ModerationLog
  AS->>AN: emit ADMIN_PREFERENCES_RESET
  AS-->>AUI: reset complete
